            <div class="about-section">
                <div class="about-title">Solo — Difficulty Guide</div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h4>🌿 Easy — 2 Minutes</h4>
                    <p>Basic hiragana and katakana only. Slow question pace. Perfect for absolute beginners. Words pulled from beginner database entries.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h4>⚡ Normal — 1:30</h4>
                    <p>Mix of kana and basic vocabulary words from the database. Moderate speed. Great for intermediate learners building fluency.</p>
